Package: rvalhalla
Title: Interface to the Valhalla Routing Engine and Accompanying Libraries
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Robin", "Lovelace", email = "rob00x@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5679-6536"))
    )
Description: Provides an interface to the Valhalla APIs, allowing users to calculate optimized routes between geographic points and undertake a range of transport network analysis tasks, including isochrone generation and map matching.
